  "notes": [
    "deck_arc 仍然是 legacy 图，metadata 明确声明 `useLegacyApi=true`，真实请求路径是 `/superset/explore_json/`。",
    "`/superset/explore_json/` 路径会读取原始 `form_data`，补 `datasource`，然后执行 `convert_legacy_filters_into_adhoc(form_data)` 与 `merge_extra_filters(form_data)`。",
    "当前源码里 `Guest user cannot modify chart payload` 只在 `security/manager.py::raise_for_access(query_context=...)` 分支触发，核心比较器是 `query_context_modified()`；legacy `/superset/explore_json/` 则会走 `views/utils.py::check_datasource_perms()` -> `get_viz()` -> `viz.raise_for_access()` -> `security/manager.py::raise_for_access(viz=self)`。当前 `viz` 分支会校验 `dashboardId` / `slice_id` / datasource 绑定，但没有等价的 columns / metrics / orderby 子集比较器。",
    "即便如此，deck_arc 的起点/终点空间配置、地图样式、viewport、配色模式和自定义 JS 都直接来自 root form_data。最稳妥的 embedding 策略仍然是根层复制保存态图表，只把动态筛选放进 `extra_form_data`。",
    "`crossFiltersDataMask.ts` 对 deck_arc 会根据 `start_spatial` 与 `end_spatial` 同时生成过滤条件，并把结果放到 `extraFormData.filters`。这说明对 deck_arc 来说，`extra_form_data.filters` 是高置信、源码证实的动态筛选容器。",
    "如果保存态图表里已经带有 legacy 时间字段 `granularity_sqla/time_grain_sqla/time_range`，guest embedding 最稳妥的做法也是原样复制；不要在 embedding 请求里自行增删这些字段。"
  ],
  "security_enforcement": {
    "frontend_request_mode": "legacy explore_json",
    "frontend_request_endpoint": "/superset/explore_json/",
    "frontend_request_payload": {
      "form_data": "<raw form_data>"
    },
    "backend_normalization_steps": [
      "convert_legacy_filters_into_adhoc(form_data)",
      "merge_extra_filters(form_data)"
    ],
    "verified_guest_payload_guard": {
      "chart_data_api": "security/manager.py::query_context_modified",
      "chart_data_api_error": "Guest user cannot modify chart payload",
      "legacy_explore_json_api": "`check_datasource_perms()` 会构造 viz 并调用 `raise_for_access(viz=self)`；该分支校验 datasource / dashboard / slice 绑定，但没有 `query_context_modified()` 那种 query subset guard",
      "confidence": "high"
    },
    "guest_access_binding_fields": [
