      "color_scheme_type",
      "color_picker",
      "target_color_picker",
      "dimension",
      "color_scheme",
      "stroke_width",
      "legend_position",
      "legend_format",
      "js_columns",
      "js_data_mutator",
      "js_tooltip",
      "js_onclick_href",
      "granularity_sqla/time_grain_sqla/time_range (if present in saved chart)",
      "all other saved chart-definition fields"
    ],
    "why": [
      "deck_arc 没有专属前端 buildQuery，前端会把 root form_data 直接发给 `/superset/explore_json/`。",
      "`BaseDeckGLViz.query_obj()` / `DeckArc.query_obj()` 会直接消费 root `start_spatial`、`end_spatial`、`filter_nulls`、`adhoc_filters` 和可选 `dimension`、`js_columns`。",
      "`Arc.tsx` / `common.tsx` 会直接消费 root `mapbox_style`、`viewport`、`color_scheme_type`、`stroke_width`、配色字段和自定义 JS 字段。",
      "`merge_extra_filters()` 会在后端把 `extra_form_data` 并入 legacy 请求，因此动态筛选不需要通过覆盖根层保存态字段来实现。",
      "虽然当前没有在 legacy 路径定位到 `query_context_modified()` 等价校验，但复制保存态仍然是最稳妥、最接近官方前端行为的策略。"
    ]
  },
